title: Garen skin redeem code isn't working!
body: My redeem code doesn't want to work! It says: There was a problem fulfilling your store items, please try again! Can you help me, please?

replies.body:
Poro-bro ooooon duuutyyy!

Sometimes those codes just don't want to work correctly is all. Be sure to double check your collection for that skin now though ^_^!
Thank you so much! Now I have it.

If you haven't done so, you could submit a ticket and request the skin to be added to your account. If you don't want to write a ticket, you can wait till one of the poros gets back, and I'm sure they'll happily help you. If you don't already have them, you could also check out and request Unchained Alistar and Riot Girl Tristana for free while you're at it.
